{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "——开业第二周的早晨。\n看到邮箱里默默塞进来的一沓账单，我头晕目眩。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（电费、水费、房租……糟了，没钱了……）"
    },
    {
      "include": "common/weekly_settlement"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（手头的钱所剩无几……客人还是只有龙姐一个。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（不过，至少有利息宽限……得感谢龙姐才行。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（……话说回来，要感谢的对象是高利贷，这算怎么回事……）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "哟。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "龙姐！您来了！"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……嗯，确实有效果。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "上周治疗之后，感觉肩膀轻了不少。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "真的吗！太好了！"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "别得意忘形。债还是债。",
      "outfit": "suit"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "closemouth",
      "text": "我、我知道……"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "text": "（不过，她承认效果了，还是挺高兴的……）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "多亏了你，我还打了3圈麻将。",
